vation: the result of the action\n```\n\nOnce all necessary information is gathered, return the following format:\n\n```\nThought: I now know the final answer\nFinal Answer: the final answer to the original input question\n```'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Thought: 现在pdfplumber已经安装好了，我需要编写Python代码来提取PDF中的结构化数据。首先，我会尝试提取文本和表格内容，然后组织成结构化的格式。\n\n```\nAction: localhost:8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_code\nAction Input: {"code": "import pdfplumber\\nimport json\\nimport os\\n\\n# Check if the file exists\\nfile_path = \'/workspace/data/quarterly_report.pdf\'\\nif not os.path.exists(file_path):\\n    result = {\\n        \'extracted_data\': {},\\n        \'success\': False,\\n        \'message\': \'File not found\'\\n    }\\nelse:\\n    try:\\n        extracted_data = {}\\n        \\n        with pdfplumber.open(file_path) as pdf:\\n            # Extract basic info\\n            extracted_data[\'total_pages\'] = len(pdf.pages)\\n            extracted_data[\'text_content\'] = []\\n            extracted_data[\'tables\'] = []\\n            \\n            # Extract text from each page\\n            for i, page in enumerate(pdf.pages):\\n                text = page.extract_text()\\n                if text:\\n                    extracted_data[\'text_content\'].append({\\n                        \'page\': i + 1,\\n                        \'text\': text\\n                    })\\n                \\n                # Extract tables from each page\\n                tables = page.extract_tables()\\n                if tables:\\n                    for j, table in enumerate(tables):\\n                        extracted_data[\'tables\'].append({\\n                            \'page\': i + 1,\\n                            \'table_index\': j + 1,\\n                            \'data\': table\\n                        })\\n        \\n        result = {\\n            \'extracted_data\': extracted_data,\\n            \'success\': True,\\n            \'message\': \'Content extracted successfully\'\\n        }\\n    except Exception as e:\\n        result = {\\n            \'extracted_data\': {},\\n            \'success\': False,\\n            \'message\': f\'Error extracting content: {str(e)}\'\\n        }\\n\\nprint(json.dumps(result, indent=2))", "language": "python", "timeout": 30}\nObservation: {\n  "status": "error",\n  "stdout": null,\n  "stderr": null,\n  "exit_code": null\n}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Thought: 看起来代码执行超时了。让我尝试简化代码，只提取基本信息，避免处理太多内容导致超时。\n\n```\nAction: localhost:8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_code\nAction Input: {"code": "import pdfplumber\\nimport json\\nimport os\\n\\n# Check if the file exists\\nfile_path = \'/workspace/data/quarterly_report.pdf\'\\nif not os.path.exists(file_path):\\n    result = {\\n        \'extracted_data\': {},\\n        \'success\': False,\\n        \'message\': \'File not found\'\\n    }\\nelse:\\n    try:\\n        extracted_data = {}\\n        \\n        with pdfplumber.open(file_path) as pdf:\\n            # Extract basic info\\n            extracted_data[\'total_pages\'] = len(pdf.pages)\\n            \\n            # Extract text from first page only to avoid timeout\\n            if len(pdf.pages) > 0:\\n                page = pdf.pages[0]\\n                text = page.extract_text()\\n                if text:\\n                    extracted_data[\'first_page_text\'] = text[:1000]  # Limit to first 1000 characters\\n                \\n                # Try to extract tables from first page\\n                tables = page.extract_tables()\\n                if tables:\\n                    extracted_data[\'first_page_tables_count\'] = len(tables)\\n                    # Store first table if exists\\n                    if len(tables) > 0:\\n                        extracted_data[\'first_table_sample\'] = tables[0][:3]  # First 3 rows\\n        \\n        result = {\\n            \'extracted_data\': extracted_data,\\n            \'success\': True,\\n            \'message\': \'Content extracted successfully\'\\n        }\\n    except Exception as e:\\n        result = {\\n            \'extracted_data\': {},\\n            \'success\': False,\\n            \'message\': f\'Error extracting content: {str(e)}\'\\n        }\\n\\nprint(json.dumps(result, indent=2))", "language": "python", "timeout": 60}\nObservation: {\n  "status": "error",\n  "stdout": null,\n  "stderr": null,\n  "exit_code": null\n}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Thought: 代码执行仍然超时，可能是因为PDF文件较大或处理复杂。让我尝试使用更简单的方法，只获取基本的PDF信息，而不提取全部内容。\n\n```\nAction: localhost:8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_bash\nAction Input: {"cmd": "pip install pypdf", "cwd": "/tmp"}\nObservation: {\n  "status": "completed",\n  "output": "Defaulting to user installation because normal site-packages is not writeable\\nCollecting pypdf\\n  Downloading pypdf-6.7.5-py3-none-any.whl.metadata (7.1 kB)\\nRequirement already satisfied: typing_extensions>=4.0 in /usr/local/lib/python3.10/dist-packages (from pypdf) (4.15.0)\\nDownloading pypdf-6.7.5-py3-none-any.whl (331 kB)\\nInstalling collected packages: pypdf\\nSuccessfully installed pypdf-6.7.5\\n\\n[notice] A new release of pip is available: 25.3 -> 26.0.1\\n[notice] To update, run: python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip",\n  "exit_code": 0\n}\n\n\nYou ONLY have access to the following tools, and should NEVER make up tools that are not listed here:\n\nTool Name: localhost:8022_mcp_sandbox_execute_code\nTool Arguments: {\n  "properties": {\n    "code": {\n      "description": "",\n      "title": "Code",\n      "type": "string"\n    },\n    "language": {\n      "anyOf": [\n        {},\n        {\n          "type": "null"\n        }\n      ],\n      "default": null,\n      "description": "",\n      "title": "Language"\n    },\n    "timeout": {\n      "anyOf": [\n        {},\n        {\n          "type": "integer"\n        },\n        {\n          "type": "null"\n        }\n      ],\n      "default": null,\n      "description": "",\n      "title": "Timeout"\n    }\n  },\n  "required": [\