n- 任务是否成功完成\nyou MUST return the actual complete content as the final answer, not a summary.\n\nBegin! This is VERY important to you, use the tools available and give your best Final Answer, your job depends on it!\n\nThought:'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': '我需要先理解用户需求，然后规划任务步骤。用户希望从PDF文件中提取关键数据并生成格式规范的Word文档。\n\n```\nThought: 分析用户需求并规划任务步骤\nAction: Save_Intermediate_Product_Tool\nAction Input: {"intermediate_product": {"需求分析": "用户需要从./workspace/data/quarterly_report.pdf中提取关键数据，并将这些数据整理成格式规范的Word文档", "任务分解": ["步骤1: 从PDF文件中提取关键数据", "步骤2: 将提取的数据整理成格式规范的Word文档"], "预期输出": "一个包含PDF关键数据的格式规范Word文档"}}\nObservation: 中间结果已保存， 可以进行下一步Thought'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': '我需要先使用pdf skill从PDF文件中提取关键数据。\n\n```\nThought: 使用pdf skill提取PDF中的关键数据\nAction: skill_loader\nAction Input: {"skill_name": "pdf", "task_context": {"action": "extract_content", "file_path": "./workspace/data/quarterly_report.pdf", "output_format": "structured_data", "expected_output_schema": {"type": "object", "properties": {"extracted_data": {"type": "object", "description": "从PDF中提取的关键数据"}, "success": {"type": "boolean", "description": "提取是否成功"}, "message": {"type": "string", "description": "操作结果信息"}}, "required": ["extracted_data", "success"]}}}\nObservation: {"extracted_data": {"total_pages": 3, "metadata": {"title": "(anonymous)", "author": "(anonymous)", "subject": "(unspecified)", "creator": "(unspecified)", "producer": "ReportLab PDF Library - (opensource)"}, "first_page_text_preview": "星云科技股份有限公司\\n 2025 年第三季度业绩报告\\n报告期间：2025 年 7 月 1 日 — 2025 年 9 月 30 日\\n发布日期：2025 年 10 月 28 日 | 机密等级：内部使用\\n一、执行摘要\\n2025 年 Q3，星云科技实现营业收入 42.7 亿元，同比增长 23.4%，环比增长 8.1%，超出市场预期\\n5.2 个百分点。净利润 6.3 亿元，净利率 14.8%，同比提升 2.1 个百分点。\\n本季度云计算业务首次突破百亿年化营收里程碑，AI 大模型 API 调用量环比增长\\n156%，企业客户数量达到 12,847 家，较上季度净增 1,203 家。海外市场收入占比提升至\\n18.3%，东南亚区域增速达 67%。\\n董事会决议：Q3 不派发中期股息，利润留存在用于 AI 基础设施建设，预计全年资本开支 28\\n亿元，同比增加 40%。\\n二、核心财务数据\\n指标\\nQ3 2025\\nQ2 2025\\nQ3 2024\\n同比变化\\n营业收入（亿元）\\n42.7\\n39.5\\n34.6\\n▲ 23.4%\\n毛利润（亿元）\\n19.8\\n18.1\\n15.4\\n▲ 28.6%\\n毛利率\\n46.4%\\n45.8%\\n44"}, "success": true, "message": "Content extracted successfully"}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': '```\nThought: PDF内容已成功提取，现在需要将这些数据整理成格式规范的Word文档\nAction: skill_loader\nAction Input: {"skill_name": "docx", "task_context": {"action": "create_document", "content": {"extracted_data": {"total_pages": 3, "metadata": {"title": "(anonymous)", "author": "(anonymous)", "subject": "(unspecified)", "creator": "(unspecified)", "producer": "ReportLab PDF Library - (opensource)"}, "first_page_text_preview": "星云科技股份有限公司\\n 2025 年第三季度业绩报告\\n报告期间：2025 年 7 月 1 日 — 2025 年 9 月 30 日\\n发布日期：2025 年 10 月 28 日 | 机密等级：内部使用\\n一、执行摘要\\n2025 年 Q3，星云科技实现营业收入 42.7 亿元，同比增长 23.4%，环比增长 8.1%，超出市场预期\\n5.2 个百分点。净利润 6.3 亿元，净利率 14.8%，同比提升 2.1 个百分点。\\n本季度云计算业务首次突破百亿年化营收里程碑，AI 大模型 API 调用量环比增长\\n156%，企业客户数量达到 12,847 家，较上季度净增 1,203 家。海外市场收入占比提升至\\n18.3%，东南亚区域增速达 67%。\\n董事会决议：Q3 不派发中期股息，利润留存在用于 AI 基础设施建设，预计全年资本开支 28\\n亿元，同比增加 40%。\\n二、核心财务数据\\n指标\\nQ3 2025\\nQ2 2025\\nQ3 2024\\n同比变化\\n营业收入（亿元）\\n42.7\\n39.5\\n34.6\\n▲ 23.4%\\n毛利润（亿元）\\n19.8\\n18.1\\n15.4\\n▲ 28.6%\\n毛利率\\n46.4%\\n45.8%\\n44"}}, "output_path": "./workspace/output/quarterly_report_summary.docx", "formatting": "professional", "expected_output_schema": {"type": "object", "properties": {"file_path": {"type": "string", "description": "生成的Word文档路径"}, "success": {"type": "boolean", "description": "文档创建是否成功"}, "message": {"type": "string", "description": "操作结果信息"}}, "required": ["file_path", "success"]}}}\nObservation: {"file_path": "/workspace/output/quarterly_report_summary.docx", "success": true, "message": "季度业绩报告摘要文档已成功创建"}\n\n\nYou ONLY have access to the following tools, and should NEVER make up tools that are not listed here:\n\n当需要完成的任务涉及以下XML 列表中的技能时，调用此工具。\n根据下方 XML 列表选择正确的 skill_name，并在 task_context 中提供完整任务信息。\n\n<available_skills>\n  <skill>\n    <name>pdf</name>\n    <type>task</type>\n    <description>Use this skill whenever the user wants to do anything with PDF files. This includes reading or extracting text/tables from PDFs, combining or merging multiple PDFs into one, splitting PDFs apart, rota...</description>\n  </skill>\n  <skill>\n    <name>docx</name>\n    <type>task</type>\n    <description>Use this skill whenever the user wants to create, read, edit, or manipulate Word documents (.docx files). Triggers include: any mention of \'Word doc\', \'word document\', \'.docx\', or requests to produce ...</description>\n  </skill>\n</available_skills>\nTool Name: Save_Intermediate_Product_Tool\nTool Arguments: {\n  "description": "Input for IntermediateTool.",\n  "properties": {\n    "intermediate_product": {\n      "description": "\\u4e2d\\u95f4\\u601d\\u8003\\u4ea7\\u7269\\uff0c\\u9700\\u8981\\u4fdd\\u5b58\\u7684\\u5185\\u5bb9\\u3002\\u652f\\u6301\\u4efb\\u610f\\u7c7b\\u578b\\uff1a\\u5b57\\u7b26\\u4e32\\u3001\\u5217\\u8868\\u3001\\u5b57\\u5178\\u7b49\\uff0c\\u4f1a\\u81ea\\u52a8\\u8f6c\\u6362\\u4e3a\\u5b57\\u7b26\\u4e32\\u683c\\u5f0f\\u3002\\u4f8b\\u5982\\uff1a\\u5217\\u8868 [\'item1\', \'item2\'] \\u4f1a\\u81ea\\u52a8\\u8f6c\\u6362\\u4e3a \'item1\\\\nitem2\'",\n      "title": "Intermediate Product"\n    }\n  },\n  "required": [\n    "intermediate_product"\n  ],\n  "title": "IntermediateToolSchema",\n  "type": "object",\n  "additionalProperties": false\n}\nTool Description: A tool that can be used to save intermediate thinking products during agent execution. \n\n✅ Supports any input type (string, list, dict, etc.) and automatically converts to string format. You can pass lists, dictionaries, or any other type directly - no need to convert manually. \n\nExamples: - String: \'my text\' → saved as \'my text\'- List: [\'item1\', \'item2\'] → saved as \'item1\\nitem2\'- Dict: {\'key\': \'value\'} → saved as JSON string\n\nIMPORTANT: Use the following format in your response:\n\n```\nThought: you should always think about what to do\nAction: the action to take, only one name of [skill_loader, Save_Intermediate_Product_Tool], just the name, exactly as it\'s written.\nAction Input: the input to the action, just a simple JSON object, enclosed in curly braces, using " to wrap keys and values.\nObservation: the result of the action\n```\n\nOnce all necessary information is gathered, return the following format:\n\n```\nThought: I now know the final answer\nFinal Answer: the final answer to the original input question\n```'}]
